title: NFL Week 14 Recap (Football 12/10)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by John Breech, Ryan Wilson and Sean Wagner-McGough to break down the Week 14 action including: Rams-Bears (2:00), Brinson's first Bird ride (10:00), Eagles-Cowboys (11:45), Bears or Cowboys to win the NFC (19:30), Steelers-Raiders (21:15), Ravens-Steelers (30:00), Panthers-Browns (42:20), Packers-Falcons (44:00), Saints-Buccaneers (48:00), Colts-Texans (52:00), 49ers-Broncos (1:00:00), DROY chatter (1:02:00), Bengals-Chargers (1:04:15), Patriots-Dolphins (1:05:25), Giants-Redskins (1:15:30), Lions-Cardinals (1:18:00) and Jets-Bills (1:20:00). 
 
To learn more about listener data and our privacy practices visit: https://www.audacyinc.com/privacy-policy
